social_posts.post_text: Your daily dose of cute from Mavy boy 💙

Mavy has been too busy this week to make any posts because Mavy has been puppy sitting FOUR foster pups! Friends, please say hello to Arizona, Colorado, Dakota, and Georgia. They are 10 weeks old and available for adoption soon! Look at Mavy’s stories for info on each pup. One pup is a mini me!! Apply online @happyfeetpetrescue or make a donation to support the costs it takes to save puppies like these and give them a good life 💙
If a Mavy fits, he sits. And he sits when he doesn’t fits.

Mavy’s 3rd birthday is coming up soon! This year, all Mavy wants for his birthday is to save more puppies. Mavy needs your help, friends. Since November 2022, Mavy has cared for 10 foster puppies saved by @happyfeetpetrescue but the puppies keep coming and Mavy can’t save them all. Happy Feet Pet Rescue has a network of 200 volunteers and fosters working hard to save all the puppies (and kitties!) by providing a home, food, veterinary care, training, socialization, and raising funds for medical emergencies. Right now Happy Feet has several high needs medical cases in rescue and a bajillion kittens that need to be fixed. Please help Mavy by donating to @happyfeetpetrescue or consider becoming a foster parent for a rescue in your hometown. Every little bit helps! If not Mavy, then who will save the puppies?
Just call Mavy the Comeback Kid, and maybe it can happen some day.

Mavy went to @soldanspetsupplies Doggy Ice Cream Social on Sunday. Mavy boy loved seeing all the hoomans and doggos and helped raise money for @happyfeetpetrescue !! Unbelievably, Mavy didn’t win the ice cream eating contest.. Mavy didn’t even finish his cup so he was disqualified 😂

Mavy’s first foster puppy doesn’t look like a puppy anymore! Little Leo Lion Man turns 1 year old next month! Can you believe it?! If it weren’t for @happyfeetpetrescue who knows what kind of life this adorable pibble would have. Help Mavy save more sweet pibbles and bullies by donating to our rescue @happyfeetpetrescue . Every little bit helps to pay for food, puppy shots, medication, and supplies 💙
Activate: Potato mode.

Meet Lottie (Dottie)! Her ears likes to pawty. She causes puppy trouble and is always bothering somebody. She’s just a puppy who’s in rescue. When she finds her perfect family she’ll be living life right 😎 Check out Lottie and other adorable adoptable pups @happyfeetpetrescue

Q: Which @ruffdawgtoys ball is Mavy’s favorite??
A: Trick question! They all are!
Being hoomom’s best friend is a job that Mavy takes very, very seriously. #thisissewious #momsbestfriend #bullybreed #bullylove #companionbreed #americanbully

Mavy boy is enjoying that camp life this weekend💙
💙 #beachboy #puremichigan #michiganmade #michiganders #lakehuron #americanbully #bullylife #bullybreed
That beach life tho.
That look you make when humom won’t let you back in the tent to sleep longer….
Mavy can find himself flowers…
Mavy gonna try to get those chipmunks even in his dreams!
Listen hooman. When Mavy wants to play ball, we play ball. That’s it.

This sweet girl is having a slumber party at Mavy’s house for a few days while she heals from surgery. Welcome to Mavy’s home, little Miss Paris 💕 She’s very shy, sleepy, and timid.  She loves snuggling humom, so Mavy is sacrificing snuggle time for her to feel better.
Just a happy boy!
Don’t ask questions.
Friends, do your hoomans suddenly disappear all the time when it starts to get cool outside? Mavy’s hoomans do. Mavy tries his best to be a very good boy and take care of our home.
If you look really closely, you can see Mavy’s signature side eye…
Just a few more minutes, humom.

Mavy has had a tough week, friends. First, Mavy went to the vet because his limping on his left front leg is getting worse not better. Mavy has something wrong with his shoulder and has to take lots of medicines. Then on Thursday there was a great, big scary storm. There were lots of loud noises and then it got very dark. Mavy’s beautiful backyard was ruined by big trees breaking and falling down all over. One tree destroyed the fence and now Mavy can’t play in the yard until it’s safe. Mavy’s whole family had to stay at brothers’ house for a few days until the lights came back on. But guess what. Still no playing in the yard so Mavy is big sad mad.
When Humom says she needs some beach time, we get to the beach!!

“Ozzy” is the sweetest baby boy. He will fit perfectly into a home looking for a puppy that will get along with a senior dog and/or small children. Apply to adopt @happyfeetpetrescue

Last year Leo asked Santa for a furever family and Santa delivered an adoption with @happyfeetpetrescue . What should Leo wish for this year? Mavy Boy thinks Leo should wish for Santa to bring humom some @bardogwine because fostering puppies is hard work! #bardogholiday

Ozzy and Leo have become very close over the past week. Tomorrow Ozzy has a meet & greet with an approved adopter and may be going to his furever home! Leo will probably miss the little nugget. Mavy Boy will be happy to have humom snuggles back 💯

**Meet Jameson** Mavy’s new foster pup arrived last night. He’s still getting used to the sights and sounds of a home, but Mavy and Leo will teach him how to be the goodest boy and hopefully help him find his furever family before Christmas!! Apply to adopt Jameson @happyfeetpetrescue

Leo, Mavy, and Goose are praying for our UK Bully friends 💛 We pray that people will see the light before the darkest day begins.

Mavy’s first full year being a foster family for @happyfeetpetrescue he helped take care and get adopted almost 20 puppies! While they are all special and it’s a little sad to say goodbye, it always feels good to see them going home (plus Mavy gets his humom’s lap and his favorite bed and toys back). Do you want to help save lives too? Ask Mavy how fostering works! You can make a difference. #belikemaverick #adoptdogs #fosteringsaveslives #savethepuppies #petrescue #adoptabledogs #fosterdogsofinstagram
